SUMMARY:UpENDing Parkinson's at Rocknasium
DESCRIPTION:UpENDing Parkinson’s at Rocknasium \nWednesdays\, 10-11:30 AM \nRocknasium is hosting UpENDing Parkinson’s\, a non-profit that provides guided rock climbing to those living with Parkinson’s. Entrance is free\, and rental gear is $10. Those interested may register as a climber here.
