SUMMARY:Open Jam Session
DESCRIPTION:Come join our weekly Jam Session at Watermelon Music\, hosted by Friends of Watermelon Music. We play a wide array of music\, including classic rock\, contemporary rock\, indie rock\, pop\, folk\, blues\, and much more! All instrumentation and shill levels welcomed! \nThere is a drum set\, keyboard\, and vocal mic/amp available at the store to play on. Please bring your own amp if you need one. \nWhile technically all ages\, we recommend 18 and over. Attendance is FREE with a suggested donation of $5 to Friends of Watermelon Music.
URL:https://thedirt.online/event/open-jam-session/2026-04-08/
LOCATION:Watermelon Music\, 1970 Lake Blvd.\, Suite 1
