SUMMARY:Pub Quiz (Trivia) hosted by Dr. Andy
DESCRIPTION:Sudwerk Trivia is a free\, first come-first serve\, all-ages event. \nJoin us for a fun-filled evening of brain-teasing questions and friendly competition at Sudwerk’s Pub Quiz every Wednesday from 7-9pm! Put your knowledge to the test and gather your friends for a night of laughter and excitement. \nLocation: 2001 2nd Street\, Davis\, CA 95618 \nYou do not have to be 21+ to participate in trivia. There is no drink minimum. \n 
URL:https://thedirt.online/event/pub-quiz-trivia-hosted-by-dr-andy-2/2026-04-08/
